ys per week, with flexible scheduling.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe represent international fashion designers and work closely with top retailers like Nordstrom, Urban Outfitters, Bloomingdale’s, and more. Our intern will gain hands-on experience in wholesale fashion sales, boutique operations, and the inner workings of a fast-paced showroom.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThis is a great opportunity to:\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e● Work directly with buyers and designers\u003cbr/\u003e● Get a behind-the-scenes look at both wholesale and boutique sales\u003cbr/\u003e● Be part of a small team with real growth and learning potential\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eResponsibilities include:\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e● Helping with boutique sales and customer service\u003cbr/\u003e● Store research and email outreach\u003cbr/\u003e● Data entry into Showroom Exchange\u003cbr/\u003e● Assisting on Zoom appointments with buyers\u003cbr/\u003e● Supporting social media content and outreach\u003cbr/\u003e● Sample organization and management\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePosition Details:\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e● \u003cstrong\u003eJob Title:\u003c/strong\u003e Wholesale \u0026amp; Boutique Sales Intern\u003cbr/\u003e● \u003cstrong\u003eHours:\u003c/strong\u003e 15–20 hours/week\u003cbr/\u003e● \u003cstrong\u003ePay:\u003c/strong\u003e Hourly\u003cbr/\u003e● \u003cstrong\u003eLocation:\u003c/strong\u003e NYC-based\u003cbr/\u003e● \u003cstrong\u003eStart Date:\u003c/strong\u003e Immediate\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEmail resume and short cover letter to apply to: \u003c/strong\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:erica@babelfair.com\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eerica@babelfair.com\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e.\u003cstrong\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e@\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/babelfairshowroom/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ebabelfairshowroom\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003csection id=\"phxbrandengagement-2\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-6\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eSubscribe to Our Newsletter\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003csection id=\"phxlisthub-3\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-7\"\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/cs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good/MTQ1NTQ5OTY2NzI5ODE1NjA3/mtqwndi3ntcznze1oda1njgw-1.svg\" alt=\"Related Stories\"/\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cphoenix-hub data-group-size=\"4\" data-first-group-size=\"3\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cphoenix-recommendations config=\"{\u0026#34;siteDomain\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;fashionista.com\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;siteBasePath\u0026#34;:null,\u0026#34;size\u0026#34;:3,\u0026#34;widgetName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;tempest_list-hub_fashionista_article-page_title-not-found-1-1\u0026#34;}\" percentage_for_personalized_recommendation=\"50\" additional_personalized_slices=\"[]\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-recommendations\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cphoenix-recommendations config=\"{\u0026#34;siteDomain\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;fashionista.com\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;siteBasePath\u0026#34;:null,\u0026#34;size\u0026#34;:1,\u0026#34;widgetName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;tempest_list-hub_fashionista_article-page_title-not-found-1-2\u0026#34;}\" percentage_for_personalized_recommendation=\"50\" additional_personalized_slices=\"[]\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-recommendations\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cphoenix-footer-lo